description:
Secret Sound Presents: RAVE FOR A CAUSE 4 feat. Wooli

It's that time of year! Once again Secret Sound brings to you the holiday special that gives back. 

Proceeds will go to  Open Door Mission - Rochester, NY; made possible with support from Fanboy Promotions, Photo City Improv: Comedy & Music Venue, Extraordinary Arts LLC, Colemanfilms, sound donated by JWI, and lighting by Esdee Entertainment.

Join us as we "rave" for a cause!

Headlining the night is Rochester's very own, Wooli, who started Rave for a Cause in 2014 and who is now signed with Circle Talent Agency.

Supporting acts include BENTZ, Esdee, Illusion, ZEALOUS, & Jeriko!

TICKETS: $10/ $15 Door
18+ with valid photo I.D.
21+ full bar available. 

Ticket Availability: https://www.eventbrite.com/e/rave-for-a-cause-4-tickets-38994726276 

hard-copy tickets will be available with your local promoters tba

LOCATION: 
Photo City Improv
543 Atlantic Ave
Rochester, New York

TIME: 9:00 PM - 2:00 AM; Saturday, DEC 16, 2017
